dsDescriptionValue.value:
DeltaV_Results.txt contains the Delta-V data for all objects with perturbed orbit solutions in the Minor Planet Center dataset (http://www.minorplanetcenter.net/data).
DeltaV_Results_MB.txt contains the Delta-V data for all Main Belt objects with perturbed orbit solutions in the Minor Planet Center dataset (http://www.minorplanetcenter.net/data).
Main_Belt_Code_V3.py is the code used to create the output datasets.  It is written for Python 3.6, and requires numpy, multiprocessing, pandas packages.  It is designed to work on Unix based system (macOS/Linux).  It will not work on Windows based systems.

files.description:
DeltaV_Results_MB.txt contains the Delta-V data for all Main Belt objects with perturbed orbit solutions in the Minor Planet Center dataset on May 2, 2017.
(http://www.minorplanetcenter.net/data).
files.label: DeltaV_Results_MB.txt
